title: Doctor Kataztrofa - Powerpill  :: VHS-rip
description:
It&#039;s really cheesy, but I can&#039;t get it out of my head. To me this should have been a smash hit! TAKE THE POWERPILL!

This is a treasure! Thank you Gretchen_79! :) :) :)

(Short explanation: The only sharing user on Limewire told me the most bizarre story. Years ago, in a junkyard in Germany, he had found a dusty VHS-tape with only this musicvideo on it. I was totally astonished and amazed. Maybe it was never supposed to be released?)
